      <h1 class="main-title">Chai ki Tapri</h1>
      <p class="subtitle" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6;">
        Pull up a chair. Grab a virtual chai.<br>
        Welcome to your personal developer hangout. Discuss code, debug tricky issues, explore AI, and get startup advice with your favorite industry mentors.
